text: Bloated government bureaucracy has caused necessary infrastructure projects to languish under red tape. @POTUS' infrastructure plan breaks down those barriers through public-private partnerships and by empowering state and local leaders.
Tonight, the President laid out a clear vision for the future of America…policies that put American citizens, American business, and American jobs first. #SOTU
.@POTUS “We need only look at the depraved character of the #NorthKorea regime to understand the nature of the #nuclear threat it could pose to America and our allies.” #SOTU
.@POTUS: As we rebuild America's strength and confidence at home, we are also restoring our strength and standing abroad. #SOTU
.@POTUS: For this reason, I am asking the Congress to end the dangerous defense sequester and fully fund our great military. #SOTU

Ending chain migration and eliminating the visa lottery program are core components of the Securing America's Future Act, which enhances border security and reforms our immigration system. I'm cosponsoring that bill in the House. #SOTU
Continued industrial growth in #LA03 and across the nation is reliant on a safe, fast, and modern infrastructure system. That includes upgrading our roads, bridges, railways, and waterways #SOTU
We used to be a nation of builders and doers...when we cut bureaucratic red tape and expedite permit approvals, we can do that again. #SOTU
Historic regulatory reform is unleashing economic freedom and allowing businesses and private industry to thrive. #SOTU

.@POTUS: And we are serving our brave veterans, including giving our veterans choice in their healthcare decisions.  Last year, the Congress passed, and I signed, the landmark VA Accountability Act. #SOTU
.@POTUS "In America, we know that faith and family, not government and bureaucracy, are the center of the American life.  Our motto is 'in God we trust.'" #SOTU

This has been a year of historic economic success: 

✔ 2+ million jobs created
✔ GDP growth over 3%
✔ Unemployment at a 16-year low
✔ Massive tax relief for all Americans
✔ Dow closing above 26k for first time in history.

I’m glad to see Senate Democrats join with Republicans to end the government shutdown. Over the weekend, we’ve come to an agreement that secures a 6-year reauthorization of the Children’s Health Insurance Program (CHIP) and critical support for our military personnel.

Let's not forget. Since @POTUS was elected:

- 2.1 million jobs created
- Unemployment at a 17-year low
- GDP growth above 3%
- Dow closes above 26k
- historic tax cuts for all Americans

The #SchumerShutdown is a failed effort by Democrats to distract from the booming economy.
